{
  "stem": "18813.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 404.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we knew that maybe we would be safe here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- excuse me-- that was exactly November the 10th.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were liberated in Brunnlitz, 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "April.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, just happy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know how long the happiness is going to last.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But happy that least no German Shepherd and no sticks, and nobody is beating us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, was the factory there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to work in the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we knew that nothing is going-- know, looked like we are very busy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not busy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were doing nothing, just sitting at that chair and doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, my machine was three feet taller than I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I, I couldn't reach to the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But Schindler knew when they come to check on him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was very clever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he goes, you sit and show that you work there, do something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, nothing came out from there, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ammunition with Schindler.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was making ammunition for them supposedly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hoping.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- for freedom, that that's-- we, we had the feeling that the end is coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had the feeling that the end is coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But from where, from-- I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we knew that Cracow was taken already-- January.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember like now, January I knew German had to leave because Cracow was taken already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- I worked for about a week in his kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the communication was-- he was a heavy smoker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I can show you he smoked like that, holding the cigarette and dropping-- one puff and dropped the cigarette.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I picked it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, I learned how to smoke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never smoked in my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was talking to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
